@w0xlt if it's not to hard to find, can you add links in the description to the pull requests where the current documentation went stale?

Note that we recently updated this documentation in #33765.

There's quite a few changes here, fixes (`name` -> `model`) as well as improvements (switching from `sendtoaddress` to `send`). That's fine if I have to review it only once. But if there's going to be lots of followup changes, it's easy to overlook a mistake. So it might be better to split this into multiple commits, each fixing a limited set of issues.
